                Brewgr is now run by me, Jason Zimmerman. I try to keep up on requests and issues as quickly as I can. If you ever have feedback or need assistance please send an email to <a href="mailto:brewgr@brewgr.com">brewgr@brewgr.com</a> and I will try to get back to you ASAP.
